      "rationale": "Eight input features are used: impeller diameter, blade angle, tip clearance, rotational speed, flow rate, inlet pressure, blood hematocrit, and fluid viscosity. Feature importance analysis using permutation importance confirms all eight features contribute meaningfully to prediction accuracy."
